<h2>Meet Chef Maddie</h2>
<p>Chef Maddie grew up learning her grandmother's receipes at an early age.  When she graduated
high school, she went abroad and studied at The School of Artisan Food in London, La Cuisine in Paris,
Cook and Taste in Barcelona and Ballymaloe Cookery School in Ireland.  After refining and mastering
her skills abroad, she came home and started her own restaurant to bring her grandmothers receipes
back alive.</p>

